headline: Can Coinbase (COIN) Leverage Growing Institutional SOL Demand to Strengthen Its Crypto Custody Edge?
summary: Earlier this week, Sharps Technology, Inc. announced a collaboration with Coinbase Global, Inc. to expand its Solana digital asset treasury strategy, transferring over 2 million SOL valued at more than US$400 million to Coinbase Prime's custody and OTC desk products. The move highlights growing institutional confidence in regulated crypto infrastructure and underscores Solana's increasing appeal as a corporate treasury asset.
